item.dc:creator: @The_Outsider The Outsider
item.description:
@The_Outsider wrote:

You made the client?

It says it cannot find the path… So here’s a check list:

-Is your cache called “cache.spiral-scape”?
-Is it in the C:/ drive?
-Is there a folder inside your cache called “Maps/mapConfig.txt”?

Please note capital letters…
